{
  "stem": "4967.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And we got each a number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "They didn't tattooed us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "It was too late in the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "But as you see from my photos that I had a number.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And we were housed in the [? round ?] bungalows made out of masonite.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "There was one window and a-- and a door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "You couldn't walk into the door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "You have to bend yourself to climb in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And it was a round thing, and 10 people to each bungalow, whatever they called it, to-- to each unit was there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And they allocate where to sleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And maybe later in the day they gave us some bread-- I can't remember-- or some water soup.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "This was the favorite food to the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "Soup, free of anything, [? warm ?] water, not even salt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Then we went to register.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "Or we registered the same day because most of the people arrived to a tradesmen because commercial people, or whatever you call, clerks, business men, didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "The-- the Germans didn't need them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "They liquidated them still in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly came was tradesmen, medical people, and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the intellectual people didn't remain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were liquidated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And they start to asking people from the registration.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] This-- this Hungarian Jewish actually saved my life, Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Levy. ?] Do you want to work in the camp or you would prefer to work outside the camp?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know that we have to walk five kilometers or six kilometers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Takes an hour.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But to stay in the camp under the Germans, straight away we decided-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my father decided not to work in the camp as an electrician.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
